#

Spicy Beef and Broccoli Stir-Fry

$15.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

Stir-FryAsian CuisineQuick Meal

Description

A vibrant stir-fry packed with protein and flavor, featuring tender beef and crisp broccoli in a spicy garlic sauce.

Ingredients

  • Beef sirloin: 1 pound, sliced thinly
  • Broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Sesame oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 tablespoon, grated
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • Cornstarch: 2 tablespoons
  • Vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Green onions: 2, chopped
